name: Pattern of the wizards mount
description:
***

Moves soooo slow 
under its pattern. 
The wizard whips
with words. 
“Go! Go! You ghastly ghoul!”

It treks and tumble.
Remembering the rumble
of its own tummy. 

Once alive and past childhood.
Now back behind the comfort of a cradles wall. 

It got given a blanket,
mentioned above,
with a Escher pattern. 
It does not know
(who that is)
but it is an entertaining visual.
